# ArcSave – Smart DeFi Savings Protocol

ArcSave is a decentralized savings protocol built on Arc Testnet that helps users earn passive income on their crypto assets.

## 🚀 Features
- Auto yield optimization (testnet simulation)
- Simple deposit & withdraw system
- Transparent on-chain transactions
- Beginner-friendly interface

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Blockchain: Arc Testnet
- Smart Contracts (Planned)
- Frontend (Planned)

## 📌 Vision
To make DeFi savings easy, secure, and accessible for everyone.

## 🔮 Future Plans
- Cross-chain yield aggregation
- Mobile-friendly dashboard
- Advanced analytics tools

